Package: rSALMO
Type: Package
Title: Simulation of ecological lake models
Version: 0.2.3
Date: 2015-02-15
LazyData: yes
Depends: R (>= 2.15),
    deSolve,
    ReacTran,
    plot3D,
    RColorBrewer
Author: Thomas Petzoldt, Susanne Rolinski and Rene Sachse
Maintainer: Thomas Petzoldt <thomas.petzoldt@tu-dresden.de>
Description: Simulation of ecological lake models. The current version of the
    package contains the C implementation of the lake model SALMO-II and an
    additional macrophytethat module can be run
    in 0D (1 box), 0.5 D (2 box) and vertically resolved in 1D.
License: GPL (>= 2)
URL: http://rlimnolab.r-forge.r-project.org/
